# Example:
#     Upmix 2-channel audio to 2/2 surround using matrix4_mb.
# Input channel map:
#     0: Left
#     1: Right
# Output channel map:
#     0: Front Left
#     1: Front Right
#     2: Surround Left
#     3: Surround Right

matrix4_mb signal -3/0
:2,3 delay -10m decorrelate -s1 -m -f0.7k -l35m 5 allpass 80 0.6 :
